(LEVEL 2)

DON`T BOTHER PICKING THINGS UP ON THIS LEVEL IF YOU SEE THEM WE CAN GET THEM
LATER OTHERWISE YOU MAY GET OGRED !!!!!!!!!
LOC 4,17 PUSH LEVER
YOU WILL BE FACING WEST, A HAZE WILL COME OVER THE SCREEN, NOW PRESS THE
DIAGONAL ARROW TWICE SO THAT YOU ARE FACING E.
(THE OPPOSITE TO WHAT YOU ARE NOW FACING.)
BE VERY CAREFUL AROUND THIS SECTION AS THERE ARE TWISTERS AND TELEPORTS ALL 
OVER THE PLACE.
HAVE A GOOD SEARCH AROUND THIS LEVEL AND FIND LOC 22,10
