LEVEL 13
~~~~~~~~
GO TO PART ON MAP, IT SHOULD LOOK LIKE A SQUARE IN THE MIDDLE OF THE MAP,
WITH PRESSURE PADS ON THE FLOOR.

LOC 20,14 FACE NORTH AND MAKE SURE THE STUDS ARE IN THE DOWN POSITION.
LOC 18,16 FACE EAST AND MAKE SURE THE STUDS ARE IN THE DOWN POSITION.
LOC 20,18 FACE SOUTH AND MAKE SURE THE STUDS ARE IN THE DOWN POSITION.
LOC 22,16 FACE WEST AND STEP ONTO THE FLOOR STUDS.

NOTE: YOU WILL NOW BE TELEPORTED TO LEVEL 14.


